# xts
preprocess <- function(df) {
  df <- as.data.frame(df)
  df$month <- sapply(df[,1], function(x) {
    x <- gsub(",", "", x)
    x <- gsub(" ", "/", x)
    x <- gsub("Apr", "4", x)
    x <- gsub("May", "5", x)
    x <- gsub("Jun", "6", x)
    x <- gsub("Jul", "7", x)
    x <- gsub("Aug", "8", x)
    x <- gsub("Sep", "9", x)
    x <- gsub("Oct", "10", x)
    x <- gsub("Nov", "11", x)
    x <- gsub("Dec", "12", x)
    x <- gsub("Jan", "1", x)
    x <- gsub("Feb", "2", x)
    x <- gsub("Mar", "3", x)
  })
  df$Date <- mdy(df$month)
  df <- df[,-3]
  df <- as.xts(read.zoo(df))
}
JP <- preprocess(JP) #JP
SP <- preprocess(SP) #SP
US <- preprocess(US) #US
